title: Curiosity Rover lands on Mars
description: Curiosity Rover makes perfect landing on Mars, August 6th 2012

articles.description: The US space agency has just landed a huge new robot rover on Mars. The one-tonne vehicle, known as Curiosity, was reported to have landed in a deep crater near the planet's equator at 06:32 BST (05:32 GMT).
articles.title: Nasa's Curiosity rover successfully lands on Mars
